{"title":"Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #10: Orbea Orca Aero","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-orbea-orca-aero","date":1741629527000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-2025-bikes-orbea-orca-aero\">Cyclist Track Days 2025 bikes #10: Orbea Orca Aero</a></p>\n\n<p>Whether you’re in the market for a new bike or just want to try out some of the world’s best, <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">Cyclist Track Days</a> offer a unique experience to test the latest top-end bikes from the leading brands on the market. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Next up in our run-through of some of the incredible bikes that you can test ride at this years Track Days is the Orbea Orca Aero.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Basque brand’s aero road bike is these days ridden by the Lotto pro team with sprinter Arnaud De Lie. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>At Track Days in London you can ride the Orbea Orca Aero M30iLTD, which is the build fitted with a Shimano 105 Di2 groupset, Orbea’s Oquo brand wheels, 38mm Vittoria Corsa N.ext tyres and Orbea’s funky built-in aero toolbox. It retails at £4,599.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The Orbea Orca Aero will be at the following Track Days events:</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>17<sup>th</sup> May 2025, Lee Valley VeloPark London</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>For more information on Cyclist Track Days click <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/news/cyclist-track-days-information\">here</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong><a href=\"https://www.eventbrite.com/cc/cyclist-track-days-2025-3855053\" target=\"_blank\">BOOK YOUR TICKET HERE</a></strong></h3>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n   